SystemsBiologyWorkbench::ModuleDescriptor::ModuleDescriptor (  DataBlockReader    r )  [inline]
 

create a module descriptor from the data in the given data block reader.

The data is assumed to be at the cursor in the data block and the cursor is moved to the first object after the module descriptor.

Parameters:
r  data block containing module descriptor data.
